<title>SOUTH AFRICA: S.Africa Ozz year share, dividend rises.</title>
<headline>S.Africa Ozz year share, dividend rises.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>Shr, (cts)</p>
<p>    - headline		202.3	 vs 168.0</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		 72.5	  vs 60.0</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		   58.45	 vs 49.43</p>
<p>    Tax			 12.79	 vs 11.76</p>
<p>    Net finance income    2.59	  vs 0.09 charge</p>
<p>    Turnover		  335.74	vs 297.95</p>
<p>Full name: Ozz Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - The firm said it had decided to award capitalisation shares to ordinary shareholders registered on July 11.</p>
<p>The firm added that &quot;exciting new business proposals, some of which complement existing operations, which would enhance the momentum of the group's endeavours are being considered.&quot;</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
